QTR Line Sensor Array (8 Analog Sensors)
A0 → Sensor 1
A1 → Sensor 2
A2 → Sensor 3
A3 → Sensor 4
A4 → Sensor 5
A5 → Sensor 6
A6 → Sensor 7
A7 → Sensor 8
Digital 13 → QTR Emitter Control Pin

Left Motor Driver Connections
Digital 4 → motorL1 (Direction)
Digital 3 → motorL2 (Direction)
Digital 5 → motorL_PWM (Speed PWM)
Right Motor Driver Connections
Digital 7 → motorR1 (Direction)
Digital 8 → motorR2 (Direction)
Digital 6 → motorR_PWM (Speed PWM)

ESC / Fan (Servo Controlled)
Digital 9 → ESC Signal
Button / Sensor Input
Digital 2 → zai_medregch (Start Button Input)
Serial Communication
Pins 0 (RX) and 1 (TX) → USB Serial Communication
Baud Rate: 9600

Complete Pin Summary Table
  Pin            Function
A0–A7        QTR Sensors
13           QTR Emitter + Built-in LED
4            Left Motor IN1
3            Left Motor IN2
5            Left Motor PWM
7            Right Motor IN1
8            Right Motor IN2
6            Right Motor PWM
9            ESC Signal
2            Start Button
0/1          Serial TX/RX
